Security and Privacy Compliance:

This extension is designed with security and privacy as fundamental principles:

- All user credentials are encrypted using AES-256-GCM encryption
- No personal data is transmitted to external servers beyond the configured qBittorrent instance
- All network communications use secure protocols when available
- Comprehensive input validation prevents XSS and injection attacks
- Minimal browser permissions following principle of least privilege
- Regular security audits and penetration testing protocols
- GDPR and privacy regulation compliant data handling

Browser Compatibility:

This extension is tested and supported on:
- Google Chrome (Manifest V3)
- Microsoft Edge (Chromium-based)
- Mozilla Firefox (with WebExtensions)

