Data Processing and GDPR Compliance:

Data Controller: DevLabs ZA
Purpose: Browser extension functionality for qBittorrent integration
Legal Basis: Legitimate interest (functionality provision)
Data Retention: Local storage only, user-controlled
Rights: Users may delete all data by removing the extension

This extension processes the following data locally:
- qBittorrent server connection details (encrypted)
- User preferences and settings
- Extension usage logs (optional, for debugging)
- Torrent/magnet link URLs (temporary, for processing)

No personal data is transmitted to third parties except the user's configured qBittorrent server.